data.description: Welcome to beautiful Loma Colorado! This single-story open floor plan beauty is move in ready with a courtyard, spacious kitchen w/ granite countertops, a family room with a 2-way fireplace, and a living room all over hardwood floors. These open areas are just waiting to entertain guests or have a nice night in with the family. The primary suite boasts a new custom bathroom with a separate shower and soaking tub along with a monstrous walk in closet. 2 additional bedrooms along with an office plus a roomy 3 car garage complete the floor plan. Outside is a self-cleaning solar heated pool with waterfalls and a covered outdoor kitchen with built in grill and quartz countertop. All this plus a view of the Sandia Mountain in the fully landscaped backyard featuring all new turf. Stop by today!
